// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1149 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b68d6272-d10e-56f9-82ad-dd3e3d3a07ae

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
